  <name>SysDVR-Qt</name>
  <summary>Stream Switch games to your PC via USB or network</summary>
  <description>
    <p>SysDVR-Qt is a tiny GUI wrapper for SysDVR-Client (https://github.com/exelix11/SysDVR).</p>
    <p>To use this you need to setup SysDVR on your console first, see https://github.com/exelix11/SysDVR/wiki/Setting-up-SysDVR for more information.</p>
    <p>If you want to use the USB streaming mode make sure to copy https://raw.githubusercontent.com/exelix11/SysDVR/master/Client/linux/sysdvr.rules to /etc/udev/rules.d/.</p>
  </description>
